{"tid":1892586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"家人禁玩手機 長沙灣8歲女出走蕩商場","createTime":"2020-02-22T15:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T15:39:06.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"922e473aac990b2e89cc17c1c9a1e1515bebe946","tid":1892586,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJtOgJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJtOgJt.jpg&h=b81865e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【14:00】警方更正稱，女童8歲，案件沒有可疑，也沒有刑事成份，無人被捕，列發現迷途小童案。據稱，女童趁家人未睡醒，悄悄溜出街；又向人表示「爸爸媽媽掛住玩手機，冇人理」。<br />\n<br />\n早上7時53分，長沙灣海麗商場的保安員，接獲途人告知，發現一名3至5歲的女童徘徊，趨前查問，但她無法說明住處，保安員於是報警。女童沒有表面傷痕，稍後向警員透露，因為家人不准她玩手機，於是悄悄溜出街。警員召救護車將她送到明愛醫院檢查，初步了解女童姓郭。<br />\n稍後一名婦人神色慌張，走到商場找尋女童，在場警員懷疑她是女童母親，隨即將她帶到房署辦事處內查問，了解事件始末。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200222/HN37I3W6M3L7FHRCZHRG5YKRYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200222%2FHN37I3W6M3L7FHRCZHRG5YKRYY%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdggaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=cf430faa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200222%2FHN37I3W6M3L7FHRCZHRG5YKRYY%2F&h=87ac8304\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200222/HN37I3W6M3L7FHRCZHRG5YKRYY/</a>"},{"pid":"ab25ec887e8541df0a9ff095d12870fc04708ed6","tid":1892586,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c40f894632e64afb49a00e21167babe0a839dd1","tid":1892586,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚識教就咪撚生啦"},{"pid":"dbbd6bfaabf93b5df64c3ef06162486baa2b802e","tid":1892586,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"八碎成個呀嬸咁 恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0936efe314ad8e0622fae4f71